annotations.title: Modern Classic: Tarzan

textContent:
1oz (30ml) Gin
1oz (30ml) Campari
1.5oz (45ml) Pineapple Juice
.5oz (15ml) Simple Syrup
.5oz (15ml) Lemon Juice

Shake and pour into large glass over ice
Top Soda Water
Half Orange Wedge Garnish
